&lt;h1 class="hero-title"&gt;Karan Homayounfar&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p class="hero-subtitle"&gt;
  Data Science master's student in Bristol, building practical, real-world projects in analytics, automation, and AI.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class="hero-text"&gt;
  I like taking messy, unstructured problems and turning them into something clear, organised, and repeatable.
  Most of what I build starts from a simple question: &lt;em&gt;“Can I make this easier or smarter?”&lt;/em&gt; I care about
  structure, clean workflows, and tools that someone else can actually use.
&lt;/p&gt;

